      <title>瑞银资本计划获支持，埃尔莫蒂获挪威财富基金支付薪酬</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-gets-backing-capital-plan-ermotti-pay-norway-wealth-fund-2024-04-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威主权财富基金支持瑞银计划，通过保护投资者免遭破产，使其额外一级债券（AT1）债券（一种债务形式）对投资者更具吸引力，并签署了瑞银首席执行官塞尔吉奥·埃尔莫蒂（Sergio Ermotti）的薪酬方案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-gets-backing-capital-plan-ermotti-pay-norway-wealth-fund-2024-04-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 08:47:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
